@node "Hilfe" "Help me!"
@next "Ben—tigen"
@prev "history"


                    Help me with my GuruChart-Projekt!!

I want to make a global GuruChart for the Internet and home-people, that everone can visit
and see wich program gurus a lot.

Because of that i`ve made a script (GuruStatistix/script/GC2EMail_Eng) that gets
the needed informations from the newest GC-File
and used YAM to send the informations to me.


Don`t send me your full GC-File, it`s too big! Use my program please!
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

For the results visit my amiga-page
http://userpages.fu-berlin.de/~clemenz/indexe.html

###################################################################################
